import React, { useState } from 'react'; import './Add.css'; import Title from '../../components/title/Title'; const Add = () => { const[data, setData] = useState({ name: '', email: '', password:'', fees:'', about:'', degree:'', experience:'', speciality:'' }) const[image, setImage] = useState(); return (
<form className='p-5'> <div className='picture d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-4'> <div> {image ? <img src={image} alt=''/> : <div> <label for='upload'><i className="fa-solid fa-user p-4"></i></label> <input onChange={(e)=>setImage(e.target.value)} value={image} id='upload' type='file' hidden/> </div> } </div> <p>Upload doctor picture</p> </div> <div className='form-content d-flex gap-5'> <div className='input-container'> <div className='input mb-3'> <p className='mb-2'>your name</p> <input name='name' value={data.name} className='w-100 p-2' type='text' placeholder='name'/> </div> <div className='input mb-3'> <p className='mb-2'>doctor email</p> <input name='email' value={data.email} className='w-100 p-2' type='email' placeholder='email'/> </div> <div className='input mb-3'> <p className='mb-2'>set password</p> <input name='password' value={data.password} className='w-100 p-2' type='password' placeholder='password'/> </div> <div className='input mb-3'> <p className='mb-2'>experience</p> <select name='experience' value={data.experience} className='w-100 p-2'> <option value="1">1 year</option> <option value="2">2 years</option> <option value="3">3 years</option> <option value="4">4 years</option> <option value="5">5 years</option> <option value="6">6 years</option> <option value="7">7 years</option> <option value="8">8 years</option> <option value="9">9 years</option> <option value="10">10 years</option> </select> </div> <div className='input mb-3'> <p className='mb-2'>fees</p> <input name='fees' value={data.fees} className='w-100 p-2' type='number' placeholder='doctor fees'/> </div> </div> <div className='input-container'> <div className='input mb-3'> <p className='mb-2'>speciality</p> <select name='speciality' value={data.speciality} className='w-100 p-2'> <option value="general">general physician</option> <option value="gynecologist">gynecologist</option> <option value="dermatologist">dermatologist</option> <option value="pediatricians">pediatricians</option> <option value="neurologist">neurologist</option> <option value="gastroenterologist">gastroenterologist</option> </select> </div> <div className='input mb-3'> <p className='mb-2'>degree</p> <input name='degree' value={data.degree} className='w-100 p-2' type='text' placeholder='degree'/> </div> <div className='input mb-3'> <p className='mb-2'>address</p> <input name='adress1' className='w-100 p-2 mb-2' type='text' placeholder='address 1'/> <input name='adress2' className='w-100 p-2' type='text' placeholder='address 2'/> </div> </div> </div> <div className='input mb-3'> <p className='mb-2'>about doctor</p> <textarea name='about' value={data.about} rows='5' className='w-100 p-2' placeholder='write about doctor'></textarea> </div> <button type='submit' className='p-2'>Add doctor</button> </form> </div> ) } export default Add
